          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/677.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the skin from the <strong>mackerel </strong>and discard it, then break the mackerel up into different sized pieces, some small flakes and some larger chunks</p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once thickened, remove the&nbsp;sauce from the heat, and mix in the drained<strong> potato</strong>, <strong>mackerel</strong> and <strong>cheddar</strong> with a pinch of<strong>&nbsp;salt </strong>and<strong> pepper&nbsp;</strong></p>",
